    <element name="Umbral Form" type="Spell" source="Shadow Spells" id="ID_LM_SS_SPELL_UMBRAL FORM">
        <supports>Druid, Ranger, Sorcerer, Warlock, Wizard</supports>
        <description>
            <p>You wreathe yourself in shadow and silence, allowing you to move quickly and quietly through areas of darkness. While in this Umbral Form, you can use your bonus action to teleport from one area of dim light or darkness to another you can see within 60 feet. Additionally, creatures have disadvantage on Perception checks made to see or hear you, so long as you are not in an area of bright light. If you deal necrotic damage while in this form, the damage ignores resistances.</p>
            <p class="indent">The spell ends if you are in an area of light created by a spell of 5th level or higher.</p>
        </description>
        <setters>
            <set name="keywords"></set>
            <set name="level">4</set>
            <set name="school">illusion</set>
            <set name="isRitual">false</set>
            <set name="time">1 action</set>
            <set name="range">Self</set>
            <set name="hasVerbalComponent">false</set>
            <set name="hasSomaticComponent">true</set>
            <set name="hasMaterialComponent">true</set>
            <set name="materialComponent">Ashes from a campfire, wrapped in a black cloth, collected at dusk</set>
            <set name="duration">Concentration, up to 10 minutes</set>
            <set name="isConcentration">true</set>
        </setters>
    </element>
    <element name="Doomhound" type="Spell" source="Shadow Spells" id="ID_LM_SS_SPELL_DOOMHOUND">
        <supports>Cleric, Sorcerer, Warlock, Wizard</supports>
        <description>
            <p>You craft a ghastly hound of shadow within 5 feet of you, visible only to you and a creature you can see within range. Target creature must make a Wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, the Doomhound moves 50 feet towards the target creature, unaffected by rough terrain, even if the creature is not visible. If the Doomhound is within 5 feet of the creature at the end of this movement, it deals 6d10 necrotic damage. The target creature repeats this save at the end of each of its turns until the spell ends.</p>
        </description>
        <setters>
            <set name="keywords"></set>
            <set name="level">5</set>
            <set name="school">illusion</set>
            <set name="isRitual">false</set>
            <set name="time">1 action</set>
